- ability to change i2c address of any slave device through web interface (to avoid conflicts) - STRECH - automatically do this?
- ability to create a module for specific outlet(s) eg. light cycle module, fan cycle - See soft modules below
- ability to use sensor alerts to trigger outlets
- day vs. night settings

- Hard module types:
  - power
    - 2ch_12v
    - 4ch
    - 8ch
    - 16ch
  - camera
  - sensorHub
    - X size (small)
    - X size (large)

- Soft module types:
  - light
  - fan
  - exhaust
  - humidifier_dehumidifier
  - heating_cooling //Can be used for room or reservour, ect
  - nutrient_ph

- Sensor types:
  - soilMoisture
  - temp_humidity
  - temp //Can be used for reservour, soil, ect.
  - lightIntensity
  - reservoirLevel
  - C02
  - pH
  - flood
  - PIR
  - door
  - HID //Could be a button, potentiometer, ect.
